column2: SELECT TOP #  zoo.ra, zoo.dec, photospec.z,  photospec.cx, photospec.cy, photospec.cz,  zoo.spiral, zoo.elliptical, zoo.uncertain,  photospec.petroMag_r, pz.absMagR FROM SpecPhotoAll AS photospec  JOIN zooSpec AS zoo ON zoo.objid = photospec.objid  JOIN photoz AS pz ON pz.objid = photospec.objid WHERE   zoo.ra BETWEEN # AND #  AND zoo.dec BETWEEN # AND #  AND photospec.z BETWEEN # AND #  AND photospec.zWarning = #  AND photospec.petroMag_r < #  AND photospec.type = #  AND zoo.spiral = # OR zoo.elliptical = #  AND pz.absMagR < #
